inary round|European Cup preliminary round]]\n|result1=ECPR\n|update=complete|source=\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==References==\n*[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesg/grkchamp.html rsssf]\n\n{{Superleague Greece seasons}} \n{{1957\u201358 in European Football (UEFA)}}\n\n{{portal bar|Association football|Greece}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1957-58 Panhellenic Championship}}\n[[Category:Super League Greece seasons]]\n[[Category:1957\u201358 in Greek football]]\n[[Category:1957\u201358 in European association football leagues|Greek]]\n", "text_old": "Statistics of [[Panhellenic Championship]] in the 1957\u201358 season.\n\n==Overview==\n[[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]] won the championship.\n\n==League table==\n<onlyinclude>{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|show_limit = 5\n|res_col_header=Q\n|use_goal_ratio=y\n|winpoints=3 |drawpoints=2 |losspoints=1\n\n|team1 = OLY | name_OLY = [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]\n|team2 = AEK | name_AEK = [[AEK Athens F.C.|AEK Athens]]\n|team3 = PAT | name_PAT = [[Panathinaikos F.C.|Panathinaikos]]\n|team4 = APL | name_APL = [[Apollon Pontou FC|Apollon Kalamarias]]\n|team5 = PIO | name_PIO = [[Panionios F.C.|Panionios]]\n|team6 = PRO | name_PRO = [[Proodeftiki F.C.|Proodeftiki]]\n|team7 = DOX | name_DOX = [[Doxa Drama F.C.|Doxa Drama]]\n|team8 = PAOK| name_PAOK= [[PAOK FC|PAOK]]\n|team9 = IRT | name_IRT = [[Iraklis Thessaloniki F.C.|Iraklis]]\n|team10 = ETH | name_ETH = [[Ethnikos Piraeus F.C.|Ethnikos Piraeus]]\n|team11 = APS | name_APS = [[Apollon Smyrni F.C.|Apollon Smyrni]]\n|team12 = OFI | name_OFI = [[OFI Crete|OFI]]\n\n|win_OLY = 14|draw_OLY = 5 |loss_OLY = 3 |gf_OLY = 40|ga_OLY = 14 |status_OLY = C\n|win_AEK = 11|draw_AEK = 9 |loss_AEK = 2 |gf_AEK = 39|ga_AEK = 19\n|win_PAT = 12|draw_PAT = 7 |loss_PAT = 3 |gf_PAT = 35|ga_PAT = 19\n|win_APL = 11|draw_APL = 2 |loss_APL = 9 |gf_APL = 33|ga_APL = 27\n|win_PIO = 9 |draw_PIO = 5 |loss_PIO = 8 |gf_PIO = 35|ga_PIO = 32\n|win_PRO = 10|draw_PRO = 3 |loss_PRO = 9 |gf_PRO = 32|ga_PRO = 33\n|win_DOX = 7 |draw_D